îíŸ@16add0148ed314576146a8e76f6c2aab58b8ae23e76cd93d8d922ca3fa234a74⁄òTitle: This week in Nushell #278
Path: Nushell
Content:
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14525] added a 
``merge deep``
 command for merging nested data
fdncred added a 
``config flatten``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14621] 1
 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14639] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14635] 3
), 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14610] added a 
``view blocks``
 command for debugging Nu
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14586] tweaked polars join for better cross joins
, improved 
``view source``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14609] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14624] 2
), and reverted a few PRs (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14598] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14606] 2
)
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14636] removed 
``pub``
 on some command internals
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14632] removed unused 
``sample_login.nu``
 file
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14633] set 
``split-by``
 doc category to "deprecated"
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14626] added shape_garbage
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14625] added version info to startup banner
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14611] removed duplicate version line
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14608] fixed doc files
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14603] added missing color_config settings
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14579] moved additional env vars out of default_env and updated some transient prompt vars
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14618] removed 
``-a/-all``
 flag in du
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14617] updated shadow-rs to 0.37
Bahex 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14607] added tests for 
``path self``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14602] removed 
``content_type``
 metadata from pipeline after 
``from ...``
 commands
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14596] changed closure signature in 
``std/iter scan``
 to be consistent with 
``reduce``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14594] removed the deprecated index argument from filter commands' closure signature
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14593] added an example demonstrating accumulator as pipeline input in 
``reduce``
 docs
PerchunPak 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14601] fixed issues in the example configs
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14588] improved handling of columns with null values
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14578] added flag --coalesce-columns to allow columns to be coalesced on full joins
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14640] fixed 
``commands::network::http::*::*_timeout``
 tests on non-English systems
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14642] fixed a CI error for 
``polars profile``
